{"tid":2414373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳帆笑稱港珠澳工程若再超支：一定會返嚟立法會同大家申請撥款","createTime":"2021-02-19T10:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T11:00:33.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"78e6104c5d8b7832b34e250c5cf98b998d28eb3c","tid":2414373,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4fKsTbTEDNNOsRwRzFGGQa7YUA4=/1024x576/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5E7HQ56YEFC7ZGGJT3GYVXJT2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4fKsTbTEDNNOsRwRzFGGQa7YUA4%3D%2F1024x576%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5E7HQ56YEFC7ZGGJT3GYVXJT2A.jpg&h=2b9da03c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n立法會在建制派掌控下，港府對公帑予取予攜。立法會財務委員會今日討論港澳珠大樓15億多元的超支撥款申，匆匆地只花約半個小時就在建制派支持下通過。運輸及房屋局局長陳帆在會上未能交代所有工程的最終費用，更日後有需要再申請款，「一定會返嚟立法會同大家（議員）匯報同申請撥款。」<br />\n2018年通車的港珠澳大澳大橋，原先造價近90.5億元，如今需增撥款15.1億多元「填氹」陳帆早前在工務小組審議時承認，大橋車流量低，償還貸款能力低，甚至是「連息都還唔到」。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210219/26W2DQEAABFYZLKCKLTL7KL3NE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210219%2F26W2DQEAABFYZLKCKLTL7KL3NE%2F&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=4a19ccaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210219%2F26W2DQEAABFYZLKCKLTL7KL3NE%2F&h=dd194b42\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210219/26W2DQEAABFYZLKCKLTL7KL3NE/</a>"},{"pid":"ae4e15fb6825a63277862c986d307ad8b86ff950","tid":2414373,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:55:38.000Z","msg":"港豬oh大橋=支那長期吸血計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。不過我已經唔care，基本上宜家當交稅係交保護費畀黑社會"},{"pid":"76c1817360a0e71697adf1d34e01e2a01f7c3bbb","tid